like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:38:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a6a32645d0d66cbd375820a8482ca9cf778a1a1","tid":1226390,"uid":176840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:42:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6a390858bb0abaeef8af9b11f95a574918454d5f","tid":1226390,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"從1970年到1975年，英國警方在北愛爾蘭發射了55000發150毫米橡膠子彈，殺死了13個人，每18000發彈殺死一個人，而每800發就能重傷一個人。<br />\n<br />\n後來，軍事科技人員改進了橡膠子彈的準確性，據稱可以減少傷亡人數，但是從1987年到1993年的巴以衝突中，死在以色列的橡膠子彈之下的人數至少有20人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pansci.asia/archives/68195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Farchives%2F68195&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=fdbdc743\" target=\"_blank\">https://pansci.asia/archives/68195</a>"},{"pid":"db641aa369d08bfd58e22cf364779008efd7c07a","tid":1226390,"uid":262237,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"b80ba477f9a2b7fa5380e162f5399021ca509cf2","tid":1226390,"uid":105051,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:32:30.000Z","msg":"預咗負評，但希望樓主夠膽覆我，有無研究報告分析磚頭同鐵枝嘅攻擊性? 有嘅請你post出嚟，無嘅介唔介意做研究對象? 我都想知打中頭打中眼嘅傷害，thank you! <br />\n希望你夠膽覆，ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:44:59.000Z","msg":"Hi, 我係文科生<br />\n<br />\n1. 無影片顯示市民有用鐵枝襲擊警察局<br />\n2. 鐵枝插眼致盲同死亡率唔影響橡膠子彈的傷害<br />\n3. 如果你想提出一個論點唔該你validate你個claim，而唔係走黎問我攞研究數據<br />\n4. Unless you can&rsquo;t read, please do your own research"},{"pid":"3eadee3209d2c330c7ee8e4444dbd1c02907ce02","tid":1226390,"uid":136617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3702242f74dd010a46ed5cf2fa76e7517a036d8c","tid":1226390,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:46:16.000Z","msg":"屌警察老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces